Did you perchance enter this square last?  If that's all that's left, the solve is recorded as soon as you enter the first letter.

@RP 

I didn’t think I was taking a dig at any of the teams.  I usually remember the feel as a child and the air pressure of the dome releasing through the doors when it was time to exist.  

That enveloping gust of air and pressure.

@LY 

